data.description: Welcome to the Battle Hill area of White Plains, NY 10606! This luxurious home in Westchester County offers 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and plenty of living space. Step into elegance with an open floor plan, a gourmet kitchen with stainless steel appliances, and a cozy fireplace in the living room. The master suite boasts a spa-like bathroom and ample closet space. Enjoy outdoor living in the landscaped yard. Conveniently located near shopping, dining, and transportation, this home offers upscale suburban living at its finest. Don't miss out schedule your tour today!
